three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20June%2C%20but%20unlike%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20aren't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-enforces-new-office-hours-rule-targets-coffee-badging-compliance-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequired%20to%20come%20in%20for%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20day.%20People%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20last%20return-to-office%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20very%20close%20to%20the%20office%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20personally%20so%20worried%20about%20having%20to%20do%20another%20two%20days%20in%20the%20office%20because%20I%20can%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-still-coffee-badging-office-returning-home-linkedin-poll-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecome%20in%20and%20swipe%20my%20badge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stay%20for%2015%20minutes%2C%20and%20go%20back%2C%20so%20we%20still%20have%20some%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20return%20to%20office%20policy%20is%20being%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20carry%20out%20silent%20layoffs%2C%20as%20I've%20seen%20many%20bright%20engineers%20leave%20the%20company%20after%20the%20last%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20definitely%20terrified%20about%20what%20this%20will%20mean%20for%20them.%20A%20few%20colleagues%20have%20contacted%20me%20and%20told%20me%20they%20are%20considering%20leaving%20the%20company%2C%20even%20going%20to%20lower-paying%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20flexible%20remote%20working%20policy%20did%20not%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20productivity.%20If%20you%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20growth%20and%20drive%20people%2C%20they%20will%20always%20deliver%2C%20regardless%20of%20where%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20this%20has%20been%20sufficient%20as%20long%20as%20people%20do%20their%20jobs%20to%20their%20best.%20I%20see%20the%20value%20in%20coming%20together%20occasionally%20and%20brainstorming%2C%20but%20outside%20tha