inter-get-fit-senior-games-tips-longevity-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%2057%2C%20Madonna%20Hanna%20got%20the%20urge%20to%20sprint.%20Now%2071%2C%20she's%20a%20national%20senior%20champion%20and%20says%20she%20still%20hasn't%20peaked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skenny%40businessinsider.com%20(Serafina%20Kenny)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsprinter-get-fit-senior-games-tips-longevity-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20Discover%20New%20Blood%20Group%2C%20Solve%2050-Year-Old%20Mystery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20scientists%20from%20NHS%20Blood%20and%20Transplant%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhsbt.nhs.uk%2Fnews%2Fnhs-blood-and-transplant-led-team-discovers-new-blood-group-system-mal%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENHSBT%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%20has%20identified%20a%20new%20blood%20group%20system%20called%20MAL.%20This%20breakthrough%20solves%20a%2050-year-old%20mystery%20surrounding%20the%20AnWj%20blood%20group%20antigen%2C%20first%20discovered%20in%201972.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%2C%20led%20by%20senior%20research%20scientist%20Louise%20Tilley%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20genetic%20test%20to%20identify%20patients%20missing%20the%20AnWj%20antigen.%20This%20innovation%20will%20enable%20better%20care%20for%20rare%20patients%20and%20facilitate%20finding%20compatible%20blood%20donors.%20Tilley%2C%20who%20has%20dedicated%2020%20years%20to%20this%20project%2C%20told%20BBC%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20challenging%20to%20quantify%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20people%20who%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20test.%20However%2C%20NHSBT%20is%20the%20last%20resort%20for%20around%20400%20patients%20each%20year%20worldwide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20has%20far-reaching%20implications%2C%20benefiting%20patients%20worldwide.%20NHSBT's%20International%20Blood%20Group%20Reference%20Laboratory%20in%20Filton%20provides%20countries%20with%20antibodies%20for%20research%20and%20has%20developed%20a%20test%20that%20can%20be%20added%20to%20existing%20genotyping%20platforms.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EKey%20findings%20of%20the%20research%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnWj%20Antigen%3A%20The%20team%20identified%20the%20genetic%20background%20of%20the%20AnWj%20antigen%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20better%20understanding%20and%20treatment%20of%20rare%20patients%20lacking%20this%20blood%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMAL%20Blood%20Group%20System%3A%20The%20discovery%20establishes%20MAL%20as%20the%2047th%20blood%20group%20system%2C%20home%20to%20the%20AnWj%20antigen.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGenetic%20Cause%3A%20Researchers%20found%20homozygous%20deletions%20in%20the%20MAL%20gene%20associated%20with%20the%20inherited%20AnWj-negative%20phenotype.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfusion%20Safety%3A%20The%20study%20enables%20the%20development%20of%20new%20genotyping%20tests%20to%20detect%20rare%20AnWj-negative%20individuals%2C%20reducing%20transfusion-associated%20complications.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlood%20group%20antigens%20are%20proteins%20on%20red%20blood%20cells%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20can%20lead%20to%20severe%20reactions%20during%20transfusions.%20Philip%20Brown%2C%20a%20laboratory%20technician%20and%20leukaemia%20survivor%2C%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20discovery.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20undergone%20multiple%20blood%20transfusions%20and%20a%20bone%20marrow%20transplant%2C%20I%20understand%20firsthand%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20safer%20blood%20matches%2C%E2%80%9D%20Brown%20told%20BBC.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNicole%20Thornton%2C%20Head%20of%20the%20Laboratory%2C%20noted%20the%20international%20significance%20of%20this%20discovery.%20%E2%80%9CUnraveling%20the%20genetic%20basis%20of%20the%20AnWj%20antigen%20has%20been%20a%20major%20challenge.%20With%20this%20breakthrough%2C%20we%20can%20now%20design%20genotyping%20tests%20to%20identify%20patients%20and%20donors%20with%20this%20rare%20antigen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thornton%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726652460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F0qoettt_blood-test-generic_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-discover-new-blood-group-solve-50-year-old-mystery-6592794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20scientists%20from%20NHS%20Blood%20and%20Transplant%20(NHSBT)%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%20has%20identified%20a%20new%20blood%20group%20system%20called%20MAL.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Caste%20Survey%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20A%20Month%20For%20Women%20Among%20Congress's%20Haryana%20Promises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rs%202%2C000%20monthly%20assistance%20to%20women%20in%20the%2018-60%20years%20age%20group%20and%20a%20statewide%20caste%20survey%20are%20among%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20October%205%20Haryana%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Congress%20unit%20released%20the%20manifesto%20today%20at%20a%20Delhi%20event%20attended%20by%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Addressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20making%20seven%20guarantees%20and%20we%20will%20fulfill%20them.%20We%20have%20many%20more%20promises.%20They%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20the%2053-page%20manifesto%20to%20be%20released%20in%20Chandigarh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20promises%20are%20LPG%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20Rs%206%2C000%20pension%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20widows%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20for%20government%20employees.%20The%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20300%20units%20of%20free%20electri