urrent%20turmoil%20seems%20elusive.%20While%20dissent%20and%20disagreements%20are%20inherent%20to%20political%20discourse%2C%20they%20should%20not%20translate%20into%20anti-national%20activities.%20Ideological%20conflicts%20are%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20politics%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20should%20lead%20to%20constructive%20criticism%20aimed%20at%20improving%20public%20welfare%20policies%20rather%20than%20being%20driven%20solely%20by%20a%20quest%20for%20power.%20However%2C%20the%20current%20political%20climate%20does%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20India.%20Since%20the%20general%20election%20results%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20opposition%20has%20increased%2C%20but%20it%20is%20troubling%20to%20note%20that%20the%20opposition's%20significance%20appears%20to%20be%20diminishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20democratic%20country%20like%20India%2C%20a%20strong%20opposition%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20a%20positive%20force.%20Yet%2C%20when%20ideological%20differences%20devolve%20into%20hate%20politics%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20serious%20concern.%20Today's%20opposition%20seems%20so%20disoriented%20that%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20abandon%20truth%20and%20national%20security%20in%20favour%20of%20political%20gains.%20This%20was%20evident%20when%20opposition%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20often%20criticized%20for%20his%20short-sightedness%2C%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20present%20a%20distorted%20image%20of%20India%20overseas.%20His%20remarks%2C%20which%20frequently%20criticize%20India's%20unity%20and%20diversity%2C%20reflect%20a%20troubling%20trend.%20At%20times%2C%20he%20portrays%20Hindus%20as%20violent%20or%20intolerant%2C%20while%20other%20times%2C%20he%20aligns%20with%20Western%20perspectives%20to%20undermine%20Indian%20culture%20and%20the%20freedoms%20of%20Indian%20women%2C%20calling%20them%20myths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20failed%20to%20mention%20to%20his%20American%20audience%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20actively%20promoted%20women's%20rights.%20Instead%2C%20he%20questioned%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20BJP%20manipulated%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20and%20claiming%20that%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20were%20hacked%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20results%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20the%20EC%20had%20been%20non-partisan.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20these%20claims%20undermine%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20Such%20statements%20could%20be%20music%20to%20the%20ears%20of%20nations%20like%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20which%20have%20little%20regard%20for%20Indian%20interests%20and%20could%20use%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20further%20their%20own%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20dishonest%20and%20detrimental%20to%20highlight%20India's%20alleged%20problems%20with%20exaggerations%20and%20falsehoods%20to%20score%20political%20points%20and%20present%20oneself%20favourably%20abroad.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20underlying%20motives%3A%20Is%20this%20meant%20to%20portray%20India%20as%20a%20fractured%20nation%20and%20a%20dysfunctional%20democracy%2C%20thereby%20inviting%20foreign%20intervention%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20concerning%20are%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20comments%20regarding%20Sikhs.%20During%20his%20time%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20the%20core%20issue%20in%20India%20was%20whether%20Sikhs%20could%20wear%20a%20turban%2C%20carry%20a%20kada%2C%20or%20visit%20a%20gurdwara.%20His%20frequent%20criticism%20of%20India%20during%20his%20foreign%20travels%2C%20including%20engaging%20with%20individuals%20associated%20with%20an%20anti-India%20agenda%2C%20is%20highly%20objectionable.%20Notably%2C%20figures%20like%20Ilhan%20Omar%2C%20who%20have%20criticized%20Kashmir's%20status%2C%20align%20with%20the%20INC%20and%20Rahul's%20political%20stances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20sponsored%20by%20Friends%20of%20Democracy%20(an%20organization%20linked%20to%20George%20Soros)%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Modi%20Mirage%3A%20New%20Study%20Indicates%20a%20Decline%20in%20India's%20Global%20Reputation%20under%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20released%20on%20May%206%2C%202024%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20Indian%20elections.%20This%20report%2C%20curated%20by%20Professor%20Irfan%20Nooruddin%20of%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20Dr.%20Subir%20Sinha%20of%20London%20University%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Ritumbra%20Manuvie%20of%20Groningen%20University%2C%20synthesizes%20research%20from%20sources%20like%20Pew%20Research%20Centre%2C%20V-Dem%2C%20and%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace.%20These%20sources%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20anti-India%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20portrayal%20of%20India%20as%20a%20caste-obsessed%20society%20where%20people%20cannot%20freely%20practice%20their%20faith%20and%20where%20certain%20groups%20are%20unsafe%20is%20erroneous%20and%20misleading.%20His%20statements%2C%20which%20reflect%20the%20views%20of%20social%20media%20influencers%20from%20specific%20castes%20and%20those%20advocating%20for%20a%20separate%20Kashmir%2C%20undermine%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%20Such%20objectionable%20rhetoric%20from%20the%20INC%20only%20serves%20to%20harm%20India's%20global%20standing%20and%20its%20internal%20cohesion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20believes%20that%20affirmative%20action%20will%20revive%20the%20Congress%20Party%20in%20India.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20the%20country's%20backward%20castes%20and%20communities%20for%20their%20lack%20of%20opportunities.%20His%20remarks%20abroad%20portray%20India%20as%20a%20Brahmin-Baniya%20nexus%20where%20no%20one%20else%20can%20succeed.%20This%20narrative%20is%20misleading%20and%20undermines%20the%20significant%20efforts%20India%20has%20made%20since%20independence%20to%20uplift%20large%20sections%20of%20its%20population%2C%20who%20endured%20centuries%20of%20foreign%20rule.%20Such%20statements%20discredit%20the%20efforts%20of%20his%20party%20to%20offer%20all%20Indians%20a%20fair%20chance%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20Gandhi%20family's%20long%20history%20of%20leadership%20in%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20falsely%20accuses%20the%20RSS%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20of%20devaluing%20certain%20Indian%20languages%20and%20cultures.%20He%20claims%20that%20the%20RSS%20and%20its%20affiliates%20view%20Tamil%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Manipuri%2C%20and%20Bengali%20as%20inferior.%20However%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20overlooks%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20efforts%20to%20celebrate%20India's%20diverse%20languages%20and%20traditions.%20For%20instance%2C%20Modi%20has%20repeatedly%20hailed%20Tamil%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20languages%20and%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20promises%20to%20promote%20Tamil%20globally.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20initiated%20the%20annual%20Kashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam%2C%20a%20month-long%20celebration%20highlighting%20the%20ancient%20ties%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Varanasi%2C%20aiming%20to%20bridge%20the%20north-south%20divide%20that%20has%20been%20politically%20manipulated%20by%20some%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20UNCIRF%20(UN%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom)%20report%2C%20which%20labels%20India%20as%20a%20'country%20of%20particular%20concern%2C'%20seems%20to%20reflect%20a%20coordinated%20and%20biased%20narrative%20aimed%20at%20undermining%20India's%20rising%20status%20as%20a%20global%20power.%20Such%20interventions%2C%20often%20misguided%2C%20raise%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20understanding%20of%20India's%20cultural%20fabric%20and%20reflect%20the%20biases%20of%20those%20behind%20them.%20The%20campaign%20against%20India%20abroad%20involves%20various%20fronts%20with%20lofty%20names%20but%20similar%20motives%2C%20all%20working%20to%20tarnish%20India's%20global%20image.%20Reports%20by%20organizations%20like%20V-Dem%2C%20which%20are%20perceived%20to%20have%20a%20colonial%20bias%2C%20circulate%20in%20India's%20political%20discourse%2C%20often%20targeting%20the%20Modi%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20poised%20for%20significant%20progress%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20and%20resurgent%20India%20is%20not%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20many%20global%20powers.%20The%20year%202024%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Indian%20history%2C%20marked%20by%20attempts%20to%20erode%20nationalistic%20sentiments%20through%20slanted%20narratives%20aimed%20at%20dividing%20society.%20Despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20India%20continues%20to%20advance%20towards%20its%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%20by%202047.%20The%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20INDI%20Alliance%2C%20which%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20derisively%20mocked%2C%20have%20adopted%20divisive%20narratives%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20leaders.%20This%20stance%20is%20particularly%20intriguing%20given%20India's%20commitment%20to%20pluralism%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20approach%2C%20driven%20by%20divisive%20and%20appeasement%20politics%2C%20ultimately%20harms%20both%20the%20Hindu%20community%20and%20the%20nation.%20A%20leadership%20that%20represents%20all%20Indians%2C%20rather%20than%20specific%20communities%2C%20is%20essential.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20reveal%20political%20immaturity%20and%20an%20anti-national%20agenda.%20His%20statements%20on%20global%20platforms%20seem%20more%20focused%20on%20scoring%20political%20points%20rather%20than%20fostering%20constructive%20dialogue.%20His%20actions%20raise%20doubts%20about%20whether%20he%20aims%20to%20promote%20or%20tarnish%20India's%20image%20for%20personal%20gain.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20oppose%20such%20divisive%20politics%20to%20protect%20India's%20democracy%20and%20cultural%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rajiv%20Tuli%20is%20a%20columnist%20and%20commentator%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Barthwal%20teaches%20Political%20Science%20at%20Sri%20Aurobindo%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726651380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fdgsm6th_rahul-gandhi-georgetown_625x300_10_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-rhetoric-dents-indias-global-image-6592700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20politics%20has%20reached%20a%20critical%20juncture%2C%20where%20finding%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20current%20turmoil%20seems%20elusive.%20While%20dissent%20and%20disagreements%20are%20inherent%20to%20political%20discourse%2C%20they%20should%20not%20translate%20into%20anti-national%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20reality%20TV%20show%20became%20the%20pivotal%20demographic%20in%20the%202024%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rose%20being%20submitted%20into%20ballot%20box%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e089a1a0ff598b26664633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20iStock%3B%20Natalie%20Ammari%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Higgins%2C%2035%2C%20could%20be%20your%20prototypical%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharming%2C%20handsome%2C%20and%20well%20spoken%2C%20Higgins%20uses%20his%20work%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fgenerous-coffee-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneur%20and%20philanthropist%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20fight%20poverty.%20He's%20also%20an%20independent%20who%20doesn't%20identify%20strongly%20with%20either%20side%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20topic%20by%20topic%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20much%20understanding%20the%20issue%2C%20hearing%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20issue%2C%20hearing%20why%20people%20believe%20what%20they%20believe%2C%20and%20then%20trying%20to%20make%20logical%2C%20rational%20solutions%20and%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Higgins'%20name%20sounds%20familiar%2C%20it's%20probably%20because%20you%20saw%20him%20on%20television%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20during%20a%20debate.%20Higgins%20served%20as%20the%2020th%20American%20Bachelor%20on%20ABC's%20long-running%20and%20wildly%20popular%20romance%20reality%20show.%20Higgins%20did%20somewhat%20attempt%20to%20use%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20jumping-off%20point%20into%20politics%3B%20back%20in%202016%2C%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fben-higgins-bachelor-congress%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiven%20the%20opportunity%20to%20run%20for%20state%20representative%20in%20Colorado%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20working%20on%20his%20own%20spinoff%20show.%20But%20that%20bid%20was%20incredibly%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20ran%20into%20issues%20over%20time%2C%20mostly%20legally%2C%20with%20how%20that%20was%20going%20to%20be%20filmed%20and%20who%20they%20were%20filming%20and%20how%20they%20were%20showing%20it.%20And%20that's%20ultimately%20why%20my%20campaign%20had%20to%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20said%20%E2%80%94%20seemingly%20nodding%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.denverpost.com%2F2016%2F07%2F25%2Fdisney-abc-forces-ben-higgins-drop-colorado-house-race%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20corporate%20overlords%20at%20Disney%2C%20which%20owns%20ABC%2C%20did%20not%20want%20to%20televise%20the%20former%20Bachelor's%20political%20ambitions.%20(The%20Disney-owned%20channel%20set%20to%20air%20the%20spin-off%20said%20at%20the%20time%20it%20had%20concerns%20broadcasting%20a%20show%20featuring%20the%20campaign%20%26quot%3Bcould%20raise%20significant%20compliance%20issues%20under%20Colorado%20election%20laws.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ben%20Higgins%20and%20Lauren%20Bushnell%20discuss%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20at%20AOL%20Studios%20in%20New%20York%20on%20March%2015%2C%202016%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9bf1dcfb7f307e57260e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBen%20Higgins%20tried%20to%20parlay%20his%20Bachelor%20success%20into%20a%20political%20career%2C%20but%20the%20campaign%20didn't%20last%20long.%3Cp%3EMireya%20Acierto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBachelor%20Nation's%20aversion%20to%20comingling%20political%20ambitions%20with%20the%20TV%20show%20makes%20some%20sense.%20Popular%20culture%20has%20for%20years%20been%20breaking%20into%20niche%20after%20niche.%20You%20can%20exist%20in%20a%20bubble%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bear%26quot%3B%20watchers%20without%20ever%20joining%20the%20masses%20watching%20%26quot%3BYoung%20Sheldon.%26quot%3B%20But%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20is%20different%3A%20It's%20perhaps%20one%20of%20our%20last%20monocultures%2C%20alongside%20stalwarts%20like%20the%20NFL.%20The%20show%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20in%202002%2C%20has%20had%20its%20ratings%20stumbles%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20it%20has%20recently%20experienced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2024%2F03%2Fthe-bachelor-joey-record-ratings-hometown-dates-abc-1235846511%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20viewership%20resurgence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20just%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fthe-bachelor-season-28-finale-ratings-abc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E6.3%20million%20people%20tuning%20in%20to%20watch%20the%20finale%20of%20Joey%20Graziadei's%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Golden%20Bachelor%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20featured%20contestants%20over%20the%20age%20of%2060%2C%20delivered%20blockbuster%20ratings%20in%20late%202023%2C%20reaching%20the%20coveted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2024%2F01%2Fthe-golden-bachelor-35-day-delayed-viewership-abc-1235805784%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18-to-49%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F05%2Farts%2Ftelevision%2Fgolden-bachelor-senior-center-watch-party.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourting%20older%20viewers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Given%20the%20franchise's%20relatively%20strong%20position%2C%20why%20risk%20that%20power%20by%20mixing%20in%20the%20messy%2C%20polarizing%2C%20and%20exhausting%20world%20of%20American%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20under%20the%20surface%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20is%20already%20a%20political%20show.%20Whitewashed%2C%20vaguely%20Christian%2C%20and%20deeply%20heterosexual%2C%20the%20presentation%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20lot%20like%20the%20median%20US%20voter%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20exact%20audience%20it's%20long%20catered%20to.%20Its%20fandom%20reaches%20across%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20the%20population%20in%20a%20way%20few%20other%20forms%20of%20mass%20media%20do%2C%20and%20the%20show%20itself%20reflects%20many%20of%20the%20broad%20sociopolitical%20themes%20in%20America.%20So%20it%20might%20be%20worth%20accepting%20the%20rose%20and%20looking%20at%20what%20the%20show%20tells%20us%20about%20the%20country.%20By%20understanding%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20can%20better%20understand%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20America%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20even%20glean%20a%20little%20insight%20into%20this%20year's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho%20will%20win%20the%202024%20rose%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGraziadei%2C%20the%20Bachelor%20who%20delivered%20monster%20ratings%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20made%20a%20cameo%20in%20February%20at%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20rose%20ceremony.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20for%20love%20on%20his%20own%2C%20Graziadei%20was%20helping%20the%20second%20gentleman%2C%20Doug%20Emhoff%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbachelornation.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fjoey-graziadei-visits-the-white-house-and-helps-the-second-gentleman-give-the-vice-president-a-rose%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresent%20a%20rose%20to%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20honor%20of%20Valentine's%20Day.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20that%20breached%20the%20fourth%20wall%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%3A%20a%20lead%20openly%20acknowledging%20and%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20politics.%20(The%20White%20House%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20collaboration.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chad%20Kultgen%20and%20Lizzy%20Pace%2C%20the%20cohosts%20of%20the%20popular%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20podcast%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Roses%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20coauthors%20of%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Win%20The%20Bachelor%2C%26quot%3B%20saw%20the%20video%20of%20Graziadei%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20they%20were%20stunned.%20Their%20podcast%20examines%20the%20game%20mechanics%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20like%20a%20sport%20%E2%80%94%20akin%20to%20its%20fellow%20monoculture%2C%20the%20NFL%20%E2%80%94%20and%20goes%20in%20deep%20with%20statistical%20metrics%20to%20analyze%20contestants'%20strategies%20and%20plays.%20Pace%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bscreamed%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20video%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20believe%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20us.%20Kultgen%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20theorized%20that%20it%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20Harris'%20people%20%E2%80%94%20you%20wouldn't%20see%20a%20producer%20or%20ABC%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20White%20House%20for%20a%20collab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever's%20part%20of%20putting%20together%20their%20propaganda%20is%20saying%3A%20We%20need%20to%20get%20'The%20Bachelor'%20in%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Kultgen%20said%20of%20the%20strategy%20by%20the%20vice%20president's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joey%20Graziadei%20smiles%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Bachelor%20mansion%20in%20a%20blue%20suit%2C%20white%20shirt%2C%20and%20black%20tie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aae0806979d7371824ff05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoey%20Graziadei%20stepped%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20and%20into%20a%20video%20with%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%3Cp%3EDisney%2FJohn%20Fleenor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20holiday-themed%20video%2C%20the%20Harris%20campaign's%20desire%20to%20court%20Bachelor%20Nation%20was%20also%20made%20clear%20by%20a%20line%20tucked%20away%20in%20a%20recent%20press%20release%20about%20its%20big%20plan%20to%20spend%20%2490%20million%20in%20August%20on%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAds%20will%20be%20targeted%20to%20high-impact%20programming%20that%20reaches%20the%20voters%20Team%20Harris-Walz%20needs%20to%20reach%20to%20win%20270%20electoral%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20includes%20local%20broadcast%20and%20cable%20programming%20and%20non-political%20programming%20like%20The%20Bachelorette%2C%20Big%20Brother%2C%20The%20Daily%20Show%2C%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Hip%20Hop%3A%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20The%20Simpsons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20political%20season%20that%20is%20awash%20in%20advertising%2C%20the%20campaign%20is%20sending%20a%20clear%20signal%3A%20The%20demographics%20it%20can%20reach%20during%20breaks%20from%20the%20rose%20ceremony%20could%20be%20key%20to%20swinging%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20on%20Bachelor%20Nation%20also%20makes%20sense%20given%20the%20franchise's%20viewership%20is%20dominated%20by%20one%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20swing%20votes%20of%20recent%20elections%3A%20white%20women.%20A%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.yougov.com%2Fentertainment%2Farticles%2F33065-bachelor-nation-profile-poll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20from%20the%20polling%20firm%20YouGov%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20about%20three-quarters%20of%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20fans%20were%20women%20and%20that%20a%20similar%20share%20was%20white.%20The%20fandom%20is%20split%20between%20younger%20and%20older%20viewers%3B%20about%20one-third%20of%20viewers%20were%20between%20ages%2025%20and%2044%2C%20while%20roughly%20one-quarter%20were%2065%20or%20older%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20past%20two%20presidential%20elections%2C%20white%20women%20were%20the%20most%20closely%20split%20demographic%20subgroup%20tracked%20by%20major%20exit%20polls.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Felection%2F2016%2Fresults%2Fexit-polls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2016%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20won%20over%2052%25%20of%20white%20women%20against%20Hillary%20Clinton's%2043%25%2C%20exit%20polls%20found%2C%20while%20Trump%20bested%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Felection%2F2020%2Fexit-polls%2Fpresident%2Fnational-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20white%20women%2055%25%20to%2044%25.%20That%20relatively%20close%20divide%20is%20set%20to%20continue%20in%202024.%20In%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center's%20most%20recent%20national%20poll%2C%20conducted%20between%20August%206%20and%20September%202%2C%20Trump%20led%20among%20white%20women%20with%2054%25%20of%20the%20vote%20to%20Harris'%2045%25.%20As%20in%20the%20exit%20polls%20from%20the%20past%20two%20elections%2C%20that%209-point%20difference%20was%20the%20smallest%20among%20the%20race%20and%20gender%20groups%20studied%20in%20the%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20close%20divide%20is%20even%20more%20apparent%20in%20key%20swing%20states.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoll.qu.edu%2Fpoll-release%3Freleaseid%3D3904%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuinnipiac%20swing-state%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20between%20September%204%20and%20September%208%20found%20a%20tight%20race%20between%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20in%20Georgia%20and%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20the%20cross-tabulations%20suggested%20that%20white%20women%20could%20be%20a%20deciding%20factor%20in%20each%20state.%20Trump%20had%20a%20strong%2064%25%20to%2031%25%20lead%20over%20Harris%20among%20white%20women%20in%20Georgia%2C%20but%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Harris%20led%20among%20the%20demographic%2051%25%20to%2047%25.%20It%20shows%20how%20this%20group%20could%20decide%20the%20next%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20rather%20than%20catering%20to%20one%20side%20of%20the%20political%20aisle%20or%20the%20other%2C%20Hulu%2C%20the%20platform%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fwhere-to-watch-the-bachelorette-season-21%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehosts%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20for%20streaming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20robust%20bipartisan%20usage.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpro.morningconsult.com%2Fmorning-consult-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorning%20Consult%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20poll%20of%2027%2C633%20people%20from%20January%201%2C%202023%2C%20to%20September%209%2C%202024%2C%20about%20half%20of%20US%20adults%20said%20they%20used%20Hulu.%20As%20for%20the%20demographics%20of%20that%20usage%2C%20about%2056%25%20of%20Democrats%20and%2055%25%20of%20Republicans%20said%20they%20used%20Hulu%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Republicans%20in%20particular%20seeing%20a%20spike%20during%20the%20most%20recent%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F2kTZh%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20using%20Hulu%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22457%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overlap%20between%20the%20swingiest%20demographic%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20audience%20suggests%20Bachelor%20Nation%20has%20value%20to%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20lead%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20tense%20history%20of%20race%20and%20religion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20can%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20country's%20politics%2C%20America's%20shifting%20landscape%20has%20also%20been%20reflected%20back%20into%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20show.%20For%20most%20of%20its%20run%2C%20the%20show%20has%20operated%20within%20a%20certain%20framework%3A%20Politics%20are%20never%20overtly%20discussed%2C%20and%20neither%20are%20hot-button%20issues%20like%20abortion%20or%20guns.%20Things%20like%20a%20nonwhite%20lead%20or%20a%20predominantly%20nonwhite%20cast%20are%20still%20relatively%20new%20in%20the%20world%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor.%26quot%3B%20It's%20also%20rooted%20in%20an%20omnipresent%20but%20barely%20visible%20sense%20of%20Christianity.%20Contestants%20are%20assumed%20to%20be%20Christian%20until%20they're%20not%20%E2%80%94%20but%20skew%20too%20evangelical%2C%20and%20you're%20edited%20to%20look%20a%20little%20less%20religious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20find%20'The%20Bachelor'%20to%20be%20very%20political.%20When%20I%20watch%20the%20show%2C%20it%2C%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20pretty%20obvious%20that%20it's%20a%20conservative-leaning%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20Natasha%20Scott-Reichel%2C%20a%20cohost%20of%20the%20popular%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20and%20pop-culture%20podcast%20%26quot%3B2%20Black%20Girls%2C%201%20Rose%2C%26quot%3B%20said.%20While%20the%20show%20might%20be%20aiming%20to%20be%20apolitical%2C%20that's%20a%20statement%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20void%20of%20diversity%20for%20so%20long%20is%20within%20itself%20a%20statement%20about%20its%20politics%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20cater%20to%20this%20Middle%20America%20that%20is%20very%20afraid%20of%20conversations%2C%20particularly%20surrounding%20race%20or%20sexual%20identity%20or%20sexual%20orientation%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott-Reichel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20however%2C%20politics%20and%20the%20contestants'%20political%20identities%20have%20begun%20to%20spill%20into%20the%20carefully%20maintained%20middle%20of%20the%20road.%20For%20the%20Americans%20who%20have%20seen%20their%20loved%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20galvanized%20out%20of%20political%20apathy%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%202016%20and%202020%20elections%2C%20it's%20a%20transformation%20mirrored%20by%20their%20favorite%20reality%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Claire%20Fallon%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cohost%20of%20the%20popular%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20podcast%20%26quot%3BLove%20to%20See%20It%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20accidentally%20helped%20kick%20off%20one%20of%20the%20first%20public%20cracks%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20veneer%20of%20apoliticism.%20Before%20the%20Bachelorette%20Becca%20Kufrin's%20season%20even%20kicked%20off%2C%20Fallon%20and%20her%20cohost%2C%20Emma%20Gray%2C%20helped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fbachelorette-premiere-garrett-yrigoyen_n_5b0837d9e4b0fdb2aa5342b6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorroborate%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Garrett%20Yrigoyen%2C%20the%20eventual%20winner%2C%20had%20been%20liking%20posts%20from%20right-wing%20Instagram%20pages.%20Kufrin%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbachelorette-becca-kufrin-garrett-yrigoyen-social-media-instagram-scandal-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efairly%20public%20liberal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20turned%20the%20whole%20viewing%20experience%20from%20a%20fairytale%20love%20story%20into%20something%20much%20more%20realistically%20American%3A%20two%20people%20who%20were%20dating%20and%20did%20not%20realize%20they%20had%20drastically%20different%20political%20views.%20That%20moment%20was%20a%20pivotal%20tiptoe%20toward%20something%20new.%20Yrigoyen%20apologized%20for%20his%20likes%20and%20discussed%20how%20it%20strained%20him%20and%20Kufrin%20as%20a%20couple.%20But%20the%20conversation%20didn't%20broach%20the%20substance%20of%20those%20likes.%20The%20couple%20split%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Kufrin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbachelorette-becca-kufrin-vote-election-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elater%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Anneta%20Konstantinides%20that%20if%20she%20were%20to%20become%20the%20Bachelorette%20again%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20she'd%20do%20when%20she%20walked%20into%20the%20house%20would%20be%20to%20ask%20everyone%20whom%20they%20voted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20in%20hell%20they'd%20show%20that%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20fan%20base%20moved%20on%20to%20its%20next%20Bachelor%20%E2%80%94%20Colton%20Underwood%2C%20a%20former%20NFL%20player%20who%20later%20came%20out%20as%20gay%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Ftv%2Fcolton-underwood-jordan-c-brown-relationship-timeline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarried%20a%20Democratic%20strategist%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Fallon%20said%20politics%20started%20to%20become%20an%20active%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20the%20parasocial%20world%20of%20its%20loyal%20fan%20base.%20Higgins%20thinks%20the%20fascination%20with%20contestants'%20politics%20and%20likes%20goes%20back%20to%20something%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20show%3A%20relatability%20(he%20believes%20this%20is%20why%20he%20was%20handed%20the%20lead%20role).%20People%20want%20to%20see%20themselves%20in%20contestants%2C%20and%20that%20includes%20some%20of%20their%20closest-held%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20are%20still%20looking%20for%20that%20relatability%2C%20and%20so%20they're%20intrigued%20with%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20like%20you%20for%20what%20I%20see%20on%20television%2C%20but%20do%20I%20like%20you%20for%20actually%20what%20you%20stand%20for%20politically%3F'%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kufrin-Yrigoyen%20situation%20was%20mostly%20quelled%20(or%20at%20least%20forgotten)%20in%20the%20court%20of%20public%20opinion%2C%20and%20as%20Fallon%20said%2C%20the%20show%20erected%20barriers%20against%20the%20rising%20tides%20of%20political%20polarization%2C%20working%20hard%20to%20keep%20itself%20out%20of%20it.%20But%20soon%2C%20the%20barriers%20were%20fully%20breached.%20The%2025th%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20in%20early%202021%2C%20featured%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Ftv%2Fmatt-james-official-bachelor-cast-meet-the-32-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efranchise's%20first%20Black%20male%20lead%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Matt%20James%2C%20who%20was%2028%20when%20the%20show%20was%20filming.%20Rachael%20Kirkconnell%2C%20the%20season's%20eventual%20winner%2C%20caused%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20controversy%20when%20photos%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20of%20the%20contestant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Ftv%2Frachael-kirkconnell-dropped-out-college-greek-life-after-she-learned-formal-racist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattending%20an%20antebellum-plantation-themed%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20years%20prior.%20The%20reaction%20was%20furious.%20James'%20and%20Kirkconnell's%20finale%2C%20broadcast%20live%20after%20the%20pictures%20had%20come%20out%2C%20eschewed%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20ending%20of%20checking%20in%20on%20the%20happy%20couple%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20two-hour%20discussion%20on%20race%20in%20America.%20The%20franchise's%20longtime%20host%2C%20Chris%20Harrison%2C%20was%20fired%20after%20defending%20Kirkconnell's%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20she%20was%20on%20a%20tour%20apologizing%20for%20them.%20A%20franchise%20that%20had%20long%20aimed%20to%20sit%20in%20a%20happy%20apolitical%20parallel-universe%20America%20unburdened%20by%20the%20country's%20often%20dark%20history%20was%20thrust%20onto%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20core%20cultural%20fault%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20moment%20where%20the%20political%20turmoil%20in%20our%20country%20created%20an%20internal%20conflict%20for%20the%20show%20that%20it%20couldn't%20really%20resolve%2C%26quot%3B%20Fallon%20said.%20Since%20then%2C%20it's%20been%20difficult%20for%20the%20show%20to%20avoid%20politics%20despite%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20steer%20away%20from%20them.%20And%20as%20Justine%20Kay%2C%20the%20other%20cohost%20of%20%26quot%3B2%20Black%20Girls%2C%201%20Rose%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%2C%20it%20took%20making%20a%20Black%20woman%20the%20Bachelorette%20%E2%80%94%20the%20well-regarded%20Charity%20Lawson%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F08%2Fthe-bachelorette-season-20-delayed-viewing-ratings-fantasy-suites-abc-1235520103%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elure%20audience%20members%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20show%2C%20which%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcollider.com%2Fthe-bachelorette-season-20-successful-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edealing%20with%20its%20own%20rating%20slump%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20much%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20America's%20interest%20in%20the%20daily%20machinations%20of%20Trump-run%20Washington%2C%20the%20fans'%20fascination%20with%20the%20contestants'%20politics%20hasn't%20evaporated%20but%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20more%20tempered.%20After%20all%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20tenure%20has%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fnewsletters%2Farchive%2F2023%2F11%2Fjoe-biden-2024-election-post-policy-era%2F676157%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitical-commentary%2Fjoe-biden-2024-donald-trump-boring-important-1234723195%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeemed%3C%2Fa%3E%20boring%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-economy-is-bidenomics-working-policies-progress-unnoticed-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarked%20instead%20by%20quieter%20policy%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20seasons%2C%20prominent%20contestants%20have%20reportedly%20liked%20right-wing%20and%20Trump-leaning%20posts%3B%20those%20revelations%20haven't%20seemed%20to%20rock%20the%20fan%20base%20as%20much%20as%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPartly%20what%20we're%20seeing%20is%20that%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20battle%20for%20cultural%20dominance%20in%20the%20form%20of%20'Bachelor%2C'%20within%20the%20franchise%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20fever%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20Fallon%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20the%20liberal%20viewers%20sort%20of%20won.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKultgen%20tied%20that%20sentiment%20to%20the%20larger%20political%20landscape.%20During%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20right-wing%20posts%20and%20sentiments%20were%20not%20given%20an%20inch%20of%20space%20because%20every%20moment%20felt%20like%20a%20crisis.%20The%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20fan%20base's%20newfound%20shrugging%20might%20reflect%20the%20cultural%20and%20political%20spotlight%20Trump%20has%20lost%3B%20he's%20a%20candidate%20who%20can%20become%20effectively%20trolled%20over%20claims%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-trolled-donald-trump-about-rally-crowd-size-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20many%20people%20are%20showing%20up%20to%20watch%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%