%20users.%20The%20company%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0xj08l9055o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20layoffs%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20just%20actively%20trying%20to%20put%20themselves%20back%20into%20the%20real%20world%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Pompilio%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20more%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260860a11-13c1-4b81-81ef-e44e7259bc1f%5C%22%3EThe%20karmic%20reward%20of%20having%20a%20wingman%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20agreed%20that%20many%20dating%20apps%20lack%20the%20energy%20they%20used%20to%20have%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she%20thinks%20the%20voice%20note%20feature%20has%20been%20popular%20with%20younger%20users%2C%20both%20in%20focus%20groups%20and%20with%20Gen%20Zers%20who%20use%20the%20app%20(a%20recent%20poll%20of%20500%20Wingman%20users%20found%20that%2069%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20used%20the%20voice%20note%20feature).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Wilson%20said%20meeting%20with%20other%20industry%20%26quot%3Bbigwigs%26quot%3B%20before%20Wingman's%20launch%20in%202017%20was%20a%20bit%20disheartening%20because%20they%20told%20her%20the%20concept%20of%20friends%20setting%20up%20dates%20would%20never%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20like%2C%20no%20one%20will%20spend%20time%20helping%20another%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFundamentally%2C%20people%20are%20too%20selfish%2C%20and%20unless%20there's%20something%20in%20it%20for%20them%2C%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it.%20And%20I%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20you%20must%20just%20have%20horrible%20friends.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20believes%20these%20founders%20were%20wrong%20because%20Gen%20Zers%20enjoy%20the%20%26quot%3Bkarmic%20reward%26quot%3B%20of%20Wingman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20cheesy%20as%20it%20sounds%2C%20people%20are%20repaying%20kindness%20by%20being%20kind%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20they're%20doing%20it%20for%20fun%20or%20banter%2C%20there's%20something%20to%20be%20said%20for%20wanting%20to%20lend%20a%20hand%20or%20doing%20that%20part%20of%20somebody%20else's%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20somebody%20else%20answer%20questions%20about%20your%20life%20leans%20into%20the%20authenticity%20Gen%20Z%20craves%20because%20it%20gives%20a%20better%20snapshot%20of%20who%20you%20are%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20%26quot%3Brather%20than%20this%20very%20polite%2C%20curated%20voice%2C%20which%20doesn't%20actually%20tell%20you%20very%20much%20about%20the%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20that%20someone's%20friendship%20group%20tells%20you%20a%20lot%20about%20who%20they%20are%20as%20a%20person%2C%20and%20she%20wanted%20to%20tap%20into%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20somebody%20grabbing%20a%20mic%20and%20saying%2C%20let%20me%20talk%20about%20my%20mate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20matching%20sense%20of%20humor%20is%20also%20vital%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20and%20that%20doesn't%20always%20come%20across%20in%20a%20traditional%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20the%20voice%20notes%2C%20they%20want%20to%20throw%20them%20under%20the%20bus%2C%20but%20they%20do%20it%20with%20kindness%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20profiles%20was%20a%20sister%20writing%20about%20her%20brother%20saying%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20why%20my%20brother%20Dylan%20says%20he's%20six%20foot%20because%20he's%20not.%20He's%205'%2010%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20Cuban%20heel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20posted%20a%20voice%20note%20saying%20her%20friend%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bbanging%20set%20of%20baps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20might%20listen%20to%20that%20crack%20up%20laughing%20and%20be%20like%2C%20oh%20yeah%2C%20that's%20my%20vibe%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20somebody%20is%20offended%20by%20that%20and%20offended%20by%20someone's%20friend%2C%20chances%20are%20they're%20not%20your%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20reviews%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20friends.%20Some%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20lie%20or%20exaggerate%20to%20land%20their%20friend%20a%20date%2C%20or%20others%20may%20take%20jokes%20too%20far%2C%20leading%20their%20buddy%20to%20attract%20the%20wrong%20type%20of%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Wilson%20thinks%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bwingman%26quot%3B%20encourages%20better%20dating%20etiquette%20because%20someone%20is%20watching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20is%20full%20of%20young%20people%20who%20complain%20about%20their%20dates%20being%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20because%20the%20other%20person%20wasn't%20how%20they%20imagined%20or%20they%20didn't%20show%20up%20at%20all.%20Some%20report%20their%20dates%20becoming%20abusive%20if%20things%20don't%20go%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20something%20charming%20about%20getting%20a%20glowing%20review%20from%20your%20grandmother%2C%20as%20one%20college%20student%20recently%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20got%20so%20much%20engagement%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20girls%20were%20swooning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-app-ceo-gen-z-users-friends-voice-notes-wingman-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726651035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e45888bf0250c2149339e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-app-ceo-gen-z-users-friends-voice-notes-wingman-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wingman%20CEO%20Tina%20Wilson%20thinks%20voice%20notes%20left%20by%20friends%20are%20the%20key%20to%20attracting%20Gen%20Z%20users%2C%20who%20are%20demand%20more%20authenticity%20from%20dating%20apps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-app-ceo-gen-z-users-friends-voice-notes-wingman-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DMK's%20Son-Rise%3F%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20Plays%20Down%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Promotion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmk-stalin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMK%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20state's%20Sports%20Minister%20-%20is%20set%20to%20be%20promoted%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Wednesday%2C%20indicating%20that%20a%20formal%20announcement%20is%20expected%20from%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi's%20office%20later%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20over%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20promotion%20has%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months%3B%20in%20August%20senior%20party%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20party%20is%20considering%20the%20step%20as%20part%20of%20prepping%20for%20the%202026%20Assembly%20election%20and%20to%20strengthen%20its%20second-rung%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20son%20led%20the%20DMK's%20campaign%20for%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20and%20the%20dominant%20showing%20-%20winning%20all%2022%20seats%20it%20contested%20-%20has%20added%20to%20the%20clamour%20for%20his%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20party's%20successful%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%20and%20the%202021%20Assembly%20election%2C%20in%20which%20the%20party%20swept%20133%20of%20the%20state's%20234%20seats%20and%20dumped%20rivals%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20answer%20to%20some%20(within%20the%20party)%20who%20thought%20Udhayanidhi%20lacks%20the%20experience%20and%20political%20acumen%20to%20command%20acceptance%20from%20the%20party's%20veteran%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20sources%20also%20said%20the%20promotion%20for%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counter%20the%20entry%20of%20Tamil%20actor%20Vijay%20into%20politics.%20The%20hugely%20popular%20actor%20-%20whose%20legions%20of%20fans%20have%20named%20him%20'%3Cem%3Ethalapathy%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20'commander'%20-%20launched%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Tamilaga%20Vettri%20Kazhagam%2C%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20however%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20talk%20of%20his%20elevation%2C%20saying%20that%20only%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20could%20take%20that%20decision.%20He%20did%2C%20though%2C%20say%20%26quot%3Bsome%20leaders...%20want%20me%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20too%20he%20underplayed%20talk%20of%20becoming%20his%20father's%20deputy%2C%20declaring%20%26quot%3Ball%20ministers%20in%20our%20government%20are%20'deputy%20chief%20ministers'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20expected%20promotion%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20fired%20(a%20predictable)%20volley%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20has%20slammed%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20possible%20elevation%20as%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B.%20The%20party%20also%20referred%20to%20ex%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20Karunanidhi%20-%20MK%20Stalin's%20father%20and%20Udhayanidhi's%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20spokesperson%20Kovai%20Sathyan%20also%20declared%20that%20naming%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20%26quot%3Bsignal%20the%20end%20of%20the%20DMK%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20will%20split%20ahead%20of%20the%202026%20election...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20also%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20before%20the%202021%20election%2C%20had%20said%20neither%20his%20son%20nor%20son-in-law%20(daughter%20Senthamarai%20Stalin's%20husband%2C%20Sabareesan)%20would%20enter%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20sources%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%2C%20pointing%20out%20Udhayanidhi%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bdemocratically%20elected%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20MLA.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20(then)%20is%20the%20question%20of%20dynasty%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20waved%20furiously%20at%20Udhayanidhi's%20controversial%20comments%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Beradication%20of%20'sanatan%20dharma'%26quot%3B%20last%20year%2C%20for%20which%20he%20faces%20police%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20over%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20ramped%20up%20last%20month%20after%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Welfare%20Minister%20Raja%20Kannappan%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20such%20at%20a%20public%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-sonrise-in-aug-tn-minister-lets-cat-out-of-bag-refers-to-udhayanidhi-as-dy-cm-6300766%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESon-Rise%20In%20DMK%3F%20Minister%20Calls%20Udhayanidhi%20'Deputy%20Chief%20Minister'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tried%20to%20correct%20himself%20immediately%2C%20declaring%20the%20reference%20would%20only%20be%20correct%20after%20August%2019%20but%2C%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20perhaps%20gave%20away%20another%20clue%20-%20the%20elevation%20will%20likely%20happen%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20on%20this%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20then%20suggested%20that%20while%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20(within%20the%20DMK%20too)%20that%20his%20son%20will%20succeed%20him%2C%20the%20ti