%20topped%20the%20World%20Happiness%20Report%20ranking%20for%20Gen%20Zs%20and%20under%20this%20year.%20Locals%20told%20BI%20why%20its%20capital%20is%20so%20great%20for%20young%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvilnius-lithuania-happiest-gen-z-cheap-safe-fun-tech-hub-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20Pagers%20Turned%20Bombs%20And%20Why%20Israel%20Is%20Being%20Blamed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20pagers%20exploded%20within%20seconds%20across%20the%20Lebanon%20yesterday%20in%20a%20synchronized%20attack%20targeting%20the%20US-designated%20terror%20group%20Hezbollah.%20The%20explosions%20killed%20at%20least%20nine%20and%20injured%202%2C800%20individuals%20in%20the%20country%20that%20has%20been%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20tensions%20in%20its%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20the%20political%20force%20running%20Lebanon%2C%20has%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack.%20Throughout%20Gaza%20war%2C%20it%20supported%20Hamas%20and%20exchanged%20fire%20across%20its%20southern%20border%20with%20Israel%20in%20support%20for%20its%20Palestinian%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20country%20or%20group%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20yet.%20But%20fingers%20pointing%20at%20Israel%20raise%20a%20big%20question%20over%20the%20capabilities%20of%20Mossad%2C%20the%20Israeli%20spy%20agency%20known%20for%20carrying%20out%20targeted%20attacks%20on%20foreign%20soils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPager%20bombs%20-%20a%20reality%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPagers%20are%20wireless%20low-tech%20means%20of%20communication%20that%20lost%20popularity%20in%20the%20nineties%20with%20the%20emergence%20of%20mobile%20phones.%20They%20can%20display%20text%20messages%20but%20not%20relay%20voice%20calls.%20Hezbollah%20uses%20pagers%20to%20avoid%20location-tracking%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ones%20used%20that%20exploded%20yesterday%20came%20fitted%20with%20explosives%20from%20Taiwan%2C%20reported%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%20Gold%20Apollo%2C%20a%20Taiwanese%20firm%2C%20had%20placed%20the%20order%20and%20the%20pagers%20were%20tampered%20by%20Israeli%20agents%20before%20they%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20US-based%20newspaper%20said%20citing%20unnamed%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%203%2C000%20pagers%20were%20part%20of%20a%20recent%20order%20for%20Gold%20Apollo%20that%20included%20mostly%20its%20AR-924%20model%2C%20reported%20the%20NYT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20intelligence%20infiltrated%20the%20production%20process%20of%20the%20pagers%20and%20fitted%20the%20explosives%20that%20could%20be%20triggered%20remotely%20without%20any%20suspicion%2C%20said%20news%20agency%20AFP%20citing%20a%20Brussel-based%20security%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-inside-lebanon-politics-hezbollah-iran-and-a-larger-battle-for-hegemony-6588884%5C%22%3EInside%20Lebanon%20Politics%3A%20Hezbollah%2C%20Iran%20And%20A%20Larger%20Battle%20For%20Hegemony%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMossad%20had%20been%20planning%20the%20attack%20for%20months%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%20They%20fitted%20the%20Taiwan-made%20devices%20with%20up%20to%203%20grams%20of%20explosives%20that%20went%20unnoticed%20by%20Hezbollah%2C%20it%20reported%20cited%20Lebanese%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trigger%20was%20activated%20and%20about%203%2C000%20pagers%20exploded%20when%20a%20codeword%20was%20sent%20to%20them%2C%20the%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20Apollo%20founder%20Hsu%20Ching-Kuang%20has%20denied%20making%20the%20pagers.%20He%20said%20a%20Hungarian%20firm%20named%20BAC%20that%20had%20the%20right%20to%20use%20his%20company's%20brand%20name%20were%20the%20original%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Israel%20Is%20Being%20Blamed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20Israeli%20PMO%20released%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20safe%20return%20of%20residents%20evacuated%20from%20northern%20Israel%20-%20which%20borders%20southern%20Lebanon%20-%20was%20among%20its%20war%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20blasts%20rocked%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMossad%2C%20which%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20carrying%20out%20sophisticated%20remote%20attacks%20on%20foreign%20soil%2C%20came%20under%20question%20though%20Israel%20never%20claims%20responsibility%20for%20such%20covert%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3-grams-of-explosives-per-pager-israel-complex-op-to-hurt-hezbollah-6590229%5C%22%3E3%20Grams%20Of%20Explosives%20Per%20Pager%3A%20Israel's%20Complex%20Op%20To%20Hurt%20Hezbollah%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20such%20incident%20that%20was%20linked%20to%20Israel%20was%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20top%20Hamas%20commander%20in%20Iran.%20Ismail%20Haniyeh's%20assassination%20in%20a%20blast%20at%20a%20high-security%20VIP%20compound%20in%20a%20posh%20Tehran%20locality%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20Mossad%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20(UK)%20reported.%20The%20bomb%20was%20smuggled%20in%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20NYT%20had%20said%2C%20and%20was%20triggered%20remotely%20after%20Haniyeh%20entered%20that%20particular%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMossad%20also%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20'Operation%20Wrath%20of%20God'%2C%20codenamed%20Bayonet%2C%20which%20was%20activated%20to%20avenge%20the%20murders%20of%2011%20Israeli%20athletes%20by%20Palestinian%20operatives%20at%20the%201972%20Olympics%20in%20Munich.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20operation%2C%20they%20used%20telephones%20not%20only%20to%20track%20their%20enemies%20but%20to%20kill%20them.%20A%20