%20to%20Chief%20Research%20Officer%20Bob%20McGrew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20integral%20to%20OpenAI's%20efforts%20to%20expand%20into%20multimodal%20models%2C%20heading%20up%20the%20team%20that%20developed%20DALL-E%20and%20the%20team%20that%20incorporated%20visual%20perception%20into%20GPT-4.%20Chen%20was%20also%20an%20important%20liaison%20between%20employees%20and%20management%20during%20Sam%20Altman's%20short-lived%20ouster%2C%20further%20cementing%20his%20importance%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3ELilian%20Weng%2C%20VP%20of%20Research%2C%20Safety%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeng%20joined%20OpenAI%20in%202018%20after%20working%20as%20a%20data%20scientist%20and%20software%20engineer%20at%20major%20Silicon%20Valley%20companies%2C%20including%20Facebook%2C%20Dropbox%2C%20and%20Affirm.%20%3Cspan%3EWeng%20took%20over%20the%20preparedness%20team%20after%20its%20former%20leader%2C%20Aleksandr%20Madry%2C%20was%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F07%2F23%2Fopenai-removes-ai-safety-executive-aleksander-madry-from-role.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Ereassigned%20last%20July%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20team%20is%20responsible%20for%20safeguarding%20against%20possible%20catastrophic%20risks%20related%20to%20OpenAI's%20frontier%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20within%20the%20company%20to%20consolidate%20safety%20research%20under%20Weng%2C%20who%20also%20serves%20on%20the%20board's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fopenai-board-forms-safety-and-security-committee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESafety%20and%20Security%20Committee%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20policymakers%20and%20consumers%20focus%20more%20attention%20on%20the%20potential%20security%20implications%20of%20high-powered%20AI%20models%2C%20Weng's%20role%20within%20the%20company%20is%20likely%20to%20become%20even%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EBarret%20Zoph%2C%20VP%20of%20Research%2C%20Post-Training%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZoph%20recently%20took%20over%20the%20team%20responsible%20for%20fine-tuning%20OpenAI's%20models%20following%20the%20departure%20of%20co-founder%20John%20Schulman.%20Zoph%20had%20been%20Schulman's%20only%20direct%20report%20and%20had%20already%20been%20overseeing%20the%20team's%20day-to-day%20operations.%20A%20veteran%20of%20Google%20Brain%2C%20Zoph%20has%20occupied%20an%20increasingly%20prominent%20place%20within%20the%20company%20as%20he%20works%20to%20ensure%20OpenAI's%20advanced%20AI%20models%20are%20ready%20for%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EAlec%20Radford%2C%20Research%20Fellow%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadford%20joined%20OpenAI%20in%202016%20at%20the%20age%20of%2023%2C%20leaving%20the%20small%20AI%20company%20he%20had%20started%20in%20his%20dorm%20room.%20His%20first%20major%20breakthrough%20at%20OpenAI%20came%20in%202017%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20famous%20%26quot%3Btransformer%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20created%20the%20architecture%20that%20still%20underpins%20LLMs%20today.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadford's%20idea%20to%20combine%20transformer%20architecture%20with%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20radically%20changed%20the%20research%20culture%20within%20the%20company.%20It%20led%20directly%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20OpenAI's%20later%20GPT%20models%20which%2C%20thanks%20to%20Radford's%20innovation%2C%20have%20outperformed%20most%20competing%20models.%20Radford%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20major%20influence%20on%20OpenAI's%20research%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223c37c79-2daf-4320-a240-020ccedc22a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoard%20of%20Directors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EZico%20Kolter%2C%20Board%20Member%20and%20Head%20of%20the%20Machine%20Learning%20Department%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%3C%2Fu%3E