ing-from-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%241%20billion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20just%20one%20year%20through%20remote%20work.%20And%20no%2C%20bailing%20out%20developers%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-commercial-real-estate-cre-crash-2008-gfc-delinquency-vacancy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebuilt%20too%20many%20offices%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20good%20reason%20for%20RTO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommuting%20five%20or%20more%20hours%20a%20week%20takes%20away%20time%20that%20employees%20could%20be%20spending%20on%20productive%20work.%20Not%20to%20mention%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-remote-work-from-home-commute-companies-climate-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eenvironmental%20cost%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20all%20that%20extra%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a61a3497-55c2-4576-9a43-0f94fb03454b%5C%22%3EIn-office%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20new%20workers%20who%20need%20training%20and%20mentorship%20sometimes%20miss%20out%20and%20feel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-remotely-feel-isolated-from-coworkers-quit-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eisolated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20sitting%20at%20home%20every%20day%20by%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20easier%20to%20be%20rude%20or%20thoughtless%20with%20colleagues%20when%20they're%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20a%20Slack%20message%20or%20work%20email.%20In%20person%2C%20people%20are%20often%20more%20polite%20and%20their%20ideas%20are%20communicated%20with%20more%20visual%20cues%20that%20help%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Faki-ito%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAki%20Ito%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%20brilliantly%20about%20the%20future%20of%20work.%20In%20December%2C%20she%20de