EGoldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20has%20raged%20against%20remote%20work%2C%20citing%20an%20episode%20when%20he%20ran%20into%20a%20junior%20employee%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20weekday%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%20Of%20course%2C%20Solomon%20himself%20was%20at%20the%20same%20restaurant%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20not%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20CEO%20of%20Victoria's%20Secret%20is%20allowed%20to%20work%20remotely%2C%20according%20to%20Fortune.%20Starbucks'%20new%20leader%20is%20using%20the%20corporate%20jet%20to%20commute%20to%20the%20office%2C%20while%20most%20employees%20sit%20in%20traffic%20or%20ride%20public%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-vp-distinguished-engineer-james-hamilton-profile-aws-jassy-boat-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Hamilton%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20sailed%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20boat%20for%20years%20while%20leading%20Amazon's%20cloud%20infrastructure%20efforts.%20The%20company%20has%20some%20of%20the%20best%20tech%20in%20this%20field%2C%20so%20he%20was%20certainly%20doing%20a%20great%20job%20while%20not%20in%20the%20office.%20(Last%20time%20we%20checked%2C%20in%202021%2C%20he'd%20gotten%20an%20apartment%20in%20Seattle).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249ef7ab6-2816-4441-9142-340e69e357d6%5C%22%3EBenioff's%20messy%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20Benioff%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-salesforce-billionaire-contradicts-himself-return-to-office-policies-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eflip-flopped%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20remote%20worker.%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20remote%20worker%20my%20whole%20life.%26quot%3B%20(The%20CEO%20likes%20to%20hang%20out%20a%20lot%20in%20Hawaii).%20%26quot%3BI%20