rrific%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%20listed%20the%20state%20government's%20steps%20to%20step%20up%20security%20at%20hospitals%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20questioned%20why%20contractual%20staff%2C%20and%20not%20regular%20cops%2C%20were%20on%20security%20duty%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20doctor's%20rape-murder%2C%20was%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20who%20had%20unfettered%20access%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20if%20the%20new%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20the%20hospitals%20were%20regular%20cops%20or%20contractual%20staff%20under%20the%20state%20government's%20Rattirer%20Sathi%20(night%20companion)%20programme%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20healthcare%20staff.%20Mr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20they%20were%20cops%2C%20and%20clarified%20that%20contractual%20staff%20on%20security%20duty%20was%20a%20short-term%20measure%20and%20would%20be%20replaced%20by%20regular%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20Mr%20Sibal%2C%20what%20really%20happened%20was%20this.%20The%20accused%20was%20drawn%20from%20the%20volunteer%20force.%20If%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20another%20set%20of%20contractual%20people...%20these%20contractual%20people%20will%20be%20trained%20for%20seven%20days%20and%20then%20they%20will%20be%20walking%20all%20around%20in%20the%20hospital.%20What%20is%20the%20protection%20young%20doctors%20have%2C%20particularly%20the%20women%20doctors%2C%20with%20these%20contractual%20staff%20walking%20around%20at%20night%20in%20the%20hospital%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20these%20security%20personnel%20would%20be%20deployed%20in%20addition%20to%20regular%20cops%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20face%20it%2C%20the%20crime%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20volunteer%20who%20is%20posted%20at%20the%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20then%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20hospitals%20now%20are%20not%20civic%20volunteers%2C%20but%20from%20a%20security%20agency%20the%20state%20government%20has%20hired%20and%20proper%20verification%20is%20done%20before%20they%20are%20recruited.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20if%20these%20personnel%20were%20undergoing%20psychological%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20doctors%20have%20a%20feeling%20of%20insecurity.%20They%20don't%20know%20who%20these%20people%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20CISF%20personnel%20are%20currently%20deployed%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20the%20junior%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20on%20a%20'cease%20work'%20protest%20can%20join%20duty.%20%26quot%3BCISF%20will%20be%20there%20for%20a%20short%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied.%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20the%20state%20government%20will%20make%20arrangements%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20doctors%20pressed%20that%20they%20want%20regular%20cops%20on%20duty%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20told%20the%20state%20government%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20problem%20when%20you%20entrust%20security%20to%20contractual%20staff%2C%20particularly%20in%20hospitals%2C%20where%20people%20are%20on%20duty%20for%2036%20hours%2C%20there%20is%20virtually%20no%20protection%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20there%20is%20a%20police%20outpost%20in%20every%20hospital%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNotwithstanding%20a%20police%20outpost%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20delayed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20responded%20that%20the%20state%20government%20would%20disband%20Rattirer%20Sathi%20if%20the%20court%20wanted%20that%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20the%20court%20wanting%20it%2C%20we%20are%20not%20in%20charge%20of%20governance.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20the%20court%20must%20have%20some%20confidence%20in%20the%20state%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20young%20students%20come%20to%20government%20medical%20colleges%20to%20pursue%20medicine.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20young%20girls%20straight%20of%2012th%20standard%20who%20are%20going%20to%20be%20there%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20dealing%20with%20young%20people%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-23%20years.%20They%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20protected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20in%20the%2045%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%2C%20regular%20cops%20must%20be%20on%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20great%20pleasure%20in%20abstaining%20from%20work%26quot%3B.%20They%20are%20abstaining%20because%20with%20these%20contractual%20people%2C%20they%20have%20a%20new%20source%20of%20insecurity%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20devil%20lies%20in%20the%20fine%20print.%20You%20say%20you%20will%20sanction%20funds%2C%20duty%20rooms%20are%20being%20constructed...%20the%20collector%2C%20district%20magistrate%20and%20police%20superintendent%20must%20oversee%20that%20these%20(security)%20arrangements%20are%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20SOP%20must%20be%20followed%20to%20identify%20locations%20for%20CCTVs.%20%26quot%3BThey%20must%20cover%20areas%20where%20female%20doctors%20rest%2C%20the%20bathrooms%20they%20use%20because%20these%20are%20areas%20where%20they%20are%20vulnerable.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20they%20have%20an%20SOP%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20doctors%20protesting%20against%20the%20August%209%20incident%20and%20demanding%20security%20at%20work%20have%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20and%20said%20they%20have%20been%20against%20putting%20volunteers%20with%20seven-day%20training%20on%20security%20duty.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20this%20security%20arrangement%20that%20relies%20on%20contractual%20staff%20is%20not%20suitable%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Front%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContractual%20Security%20Staff%20Under%20Scanner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20August%209%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20as%20the%20main%20accused%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20this%20workforce.%20An%20initiative%20started%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20after%20she%20came%20to%20power%2C%20civic%20volunteers%20were%20roped%20in%20to%20assist%20regular%20cops.%20According%20to%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%201.19%20lakh%20civic%20volunteers%20in%20Bengal%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criteria%20to%20be%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20are%20simple%20--%20the%20candidate%20must%20have%20studied%20till%20Class%20VIII%2C%20be%20medically%20fit%20and%20not%20have%20a%20criminal%20record.%20There%20are%20no%20written%20tests%20and%20the%20Opposition%20alleges%20that%20proximity%20to%20Trinamool%20leaders%20is%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjoy%20Roy%2C%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20RG%20Kar%20case%2C%20was%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20but%20enjoyed%20access%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20state-run%20hospital%20round%20the%20clock.%20He%20roamed%20about%20in%20a%20bike%20with%20a%20'Kolkata%20Police'%20sticker%2C%20wore%20a%20'Kolkata%20Police'%20t-shirt%20and%20often%20stayed%20at%20police%20barracks%20--%20all%20this%20despite%20not%20being%20a%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipak%20Burman%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Falakata%2C%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20that%20civic%20volunteers%20are%20recruited%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20inspectors-in-charge%20and%20sub-inspectors%20move%20around%20with%20three%20to%20five%20civic%20police%20these%20days.%20Their%20jobs%20are%20to%20run%20personal%20errands%20for%20the%20cops%2C%20extort%20money%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20run%20surveillance%20on%20Opposition%20politicians.%20And%20whenever%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20addresses%20a%20public%20meeting%20or%20attends%20a%20government%20programme%20in%20the%20districts%2C%20they%20discard%20the%20uniform%20and%20turn%20up%20as%20Trinamool%20supporters%20to%20fill%20the%20venue%20cheering%20loudly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20written%20tests%2C%20there%20are%20no%20interviews.%20Who%20decides%20who%20is%20fit%20to%20be%20a%20civic%20volunteer%3F%20The%20ruling%20party%20provides%20a%20list%20and%20the%20recruitments%20take%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20CPM%20leader%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20told%20The%20Telegraph.%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20the%20civic%20police%20are%20controlling%20the%20police%20because%20of%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20political%20bosses.%20The%20policing%20system%20has%20been%20completely%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726648860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbha0531o_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-devil-lies-in-fine-print-chief-justice-grills-bengal-on-doctors-safety-6592221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20faced%20tough%20questi