EIt%20was%20so%20peaceful%20that%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20the%20resort%20all%20to%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20dinner%2C%20we%20went%20to%20N%C3%9C%2C%20La%20Valise's%20restaurant%20next%20door%20to%20the%20resort.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nu%20restaurant%20in%20Tulum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db30411d8d2deb96b9f4ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20N%C3%9C%20restaurant%20right%20next%20to%20La%20Valise.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20many%20restaurants%20in%20Tulum%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nutulum.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EN%C3%9C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20open-air%20space.%20The%20wooden%20dining%20tables%20and%20chairs%20were%20arranged%20under%20a%20straw%20roof%2C%20and%20the%20plants%20covered%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%2C%20who%20loves%20gardening%2C%20was%20immediately%20hooked%20by%20the%20beautiful%20setting.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20found%20strange%20was%20the%20alternative%20rock%20soundtrack%2C%20which%20felt%20out%20of%20place%20in%20such%20a%20serene%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20enjoyed%20a%20few%20apps%20and%20a%20delicious%20fish.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20prawns%20at%20Nu%20Restaurant%20in%20Tulum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e07b5383b8099cf9fd381a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Campeche%20prawns%20at%20N%C3%9C.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20dinner%20with%20a%20chargrilled%20carrot%20dish.%20It%20cost%20380%20Mexican%20pesos%2C%20or%20about%20%2419%2C%20and%20featured%20long%2C%20thin%20slices%20of%20carrots%20and%20zucchini%20tangled%20up%20in%20each%20other%20and%20topped%20with%20lemongrass%20aioli%20and%20a%20garlic%20vinaigrette.%20The%20dish%20was%20refreshing%2C%20albeit%20a%20bit%20forgettable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Campeche%20prawns%20%E2%80%94%20which%20cost%20520%20pesos%2C%20or%20about%20%2426%20%E2%80%94%20made%20up%20for%20it.%20They%20were%20wood-grilled%20and%20jumbo-sized%2C%20so%20juicy%20and%20full%20of%20tender%20meat.%20The%20Taj%C3%ADn%20sauce%20served%20alongside%20them%20was%20a%20surprising%20and%20delightful%20accompaniment.%20My%20mom%2C%20who%20adores%20prawns%2C%20said%20it%20was%20among%20the%20best%20she's%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20a%20long%20day%20of%20traveling%2C%20we%20were%20ready%20for%20bed.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bed%20in%20La%20Valise%20suite%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db3142a0ff598b2665596f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20plush%20king%20bed%20in%20our%20La%20Valise%20suite.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20briefly%20stepped%20onto%20the%20balcony%20and%20admired%20the%20stars%20before%20sinking%20into%20the%20plush%20king-size%20canopy%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20looming%20deadline%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20felt%20incredibly%20relaxed.%20I%20quickly%20realized%20that%20La%20Valise%20had%20some%20real%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20strolled%20into%20the%20small%20bar%20and%20restaurant%20on%20the%20jungle%20side%2C%20where%20our%20complimentary%20breakfast%20was%20served.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22La%20Valise%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db3266a0ff598b26655af2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurant%20on%20the%20jungle-side%20property%20of%20La%20Valise.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20lobby%20and%20our%20suite%2C%20the%20space%20was%20tastefully%20designed%20with%20cream%20walls%2C%20bar%20stools%20with%20comfy%20white%20cushions%2C%20and%20hanging%20wooden%20lamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20handed%20the%20surprisingly%20extensive%20breakfast%20menu.%20Among%20the%2011%20main%20courses%20were%20chilaquiles%2C%20French%20toast%2C%20eggs%20benedict%2C%20avocado%20toast%2C%20poached%20eggs%20and%20polenta%2C%20and%20ranchero%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20we%20were%20also%20given%20the%20choice%20of%20a%20yogurt%20and%20granola%20bowl%2C%20a%20fresh%20fruit%20platter%2C%20or%20both.%20The%20breakfast%20also%20included%20coffee%20and%20fresh%20juices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20plate%20of%20ranchero%20eggs%20was%20as%20delicious%20as%20it%20was%20vibrant.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Breakfast%20at%20La%20Valise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db7b83a0ff598b26659a65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20breakfast%20at%20La%20Valise.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dish%2C%20which%20featured%20fried%20eggs%20on%20top%20of%20onions%2C%20beans%2C%20fresh%20cheese%2C%20and%20red%20ranchero%20sauce%2C%20was%20perfectly%20cooked.%20I%20loved%20the%20addition%20of%20fresh%20avocado%20and%20pickled%20onions%2C%20which%20added%20a%20burst%20of%20color%20and%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20the%20restaurant%20while%20working%20on%20a%20story%20that%20day%20and%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20service%20at%20La%20Valise.%20Occasionally%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bartenders%20or%20servers%20would%20come%20by%20to%20say%20hi.%20They'd%20often%20bring%20cold%20w