%20tough%20nature%20of%20Fed%20communications%20but%20said%20the%20central%20bank%20will%20likely%20aim%20for%20a%20more%20neutral%20perspective%20whether%20they%20make%20a%20small%20or%20large%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20becomes%20tricky%20for%20the%20Fed%20from%20a%20communications%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20Lyngen%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%2C%20too%2C%20that%20there's%20a%20chance%20of%20dissent%20within%20the%20Fed.%20If%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20it%20could%20help%20further%20quell%20markets'%20worries%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20jumbo%20rate%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20to%20suggest%20that%20everyone%20needs%20to%20vote%20in%20for%2025%20or%2050.%20So%20I%20think%20that%20could%20be%20another%20way%20to%20communicate%20to%20the%20market%20that%20it%20was%20a%20knife's%20edge%20decision%20and%20it's%20uncertain%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Lyngen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20will%20announce%20its%20decision%20at%202%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-outlook-jerome-powell-fomc-economy-recession-bmo-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726648202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9d7b3ce3009a0fac70168%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-outlook-jerome-powell-fomc-economy-recession-bmo-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20market%20prices%20in%20upwards%20of%20an%2080%25%20chance%20of%20a%2050%20basis%20point%20cut%2C%20the%20Fed%20will%20likely%20follow%20through%2C%20BMO%20strategist%20Ian%20Lyngen%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kcloonan%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Cloonan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-outlook-jerome-powell-fomc-econ