irked%20the%20gangster.%20Around%20this%20time%2C%20Bishnoi%20was%20taken%20into%20police%20custody%20and%20allegedly%20tortured%20and%20he%20held%20Chhabra%20and%20Shah%20responsible%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20call%20five%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Bishnoi%20told%20him%20that%20now%20he%20doesn't%20want%20money%20but%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20Rs%2010%20crore%20now%2C%20I%20want%20you%20dead.%20Get%20your%20bier%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhabra%20also%20said%20that%20his%20gang%20members%20told%20him%20that%20they%20knew%20everything%20about%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20where%20my%20brother%20works%20to%20what%20I%20do%2C%20they%20said%20they%20know%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20recordings%2C%20which%20I%20had%20shared%20with%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20when%20he%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20them%2C%20they%20told%20him%20that%20all%20this%20would%20be%20kept%20discreet%20and%20that%20he%20would%20be%20given%20police%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20happened%20for%20a%20year%20and%20then%20they%20took%20away%20my%20security%20and%20nobody%20looked%20after%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Chhabra%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20residing%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20death%20threats%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20trying%20to%20relocate%20my%20family%20too%20because%20life%20has%20no%20value%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20scared%20after%20Nadir's%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhabra%2C%20who%20has%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20against%20him%20in%20Delhi%2C%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20any%20case%20registered%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726646040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%