give%20Chinese%20armed%20forces%20the%20ability%20to%20speedily%20move%20in%20military%20resources%20into%20an%20under-developed%2C%20remote%20area%20along%20the%20Indo-Chinese%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heliport%2C%20images%20of%20which%20appear%20in%20this%20report%2C%20lies%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Gongrigabu%20Qu%20river%20in%20the%20Nyingchi%20Prefecture%20of%20the%20Tibet%20Autonomous%20Region.%20This%20is%20within%20Chinese%20territory%20that%20India%20does%20not%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen-source%20satellite%20imagery%20available%20on%20EOS%20Data%20Analytics%20shows%20that%20till%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20there%20was%20no%20construction%20at%20the%20site%20where%20the%20heliport%20is%20being%20constructed.%20A%20subsequent%20satellite%20image%20dated%20December%2031%2C%20shows%20land%20being%20cleared%20for%20construction.%20The%20latest%20Maxar-sourced%20high-resolution%20images%2C%20shot%20on%20September%2016%2C%20indicate%20that%20the%20facility%20is%20in%20an%20advanced%20state%20of%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeospatial%20intelligence%20experts%20such%20as%20Damien%20Symon%20who%20first%20highlighted%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20heliport%20point%20out%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20new%20heliport%20will%20allow%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20to%20intensify%20intelligence-gathering%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20activities.%26quot%3B%20This%20closes%20logistical%20challenges%20in%20the%20densely%20forested%20region%20which%20features%20rugged%20mountains%20that%20make%20military%20movement%20cumbersome.%20The%20construction%20of%20the%20heliport%20%26quot%3Benables%20rapid%20troop%20deployment%20to%20distant%20areas%2C%20strengthening%20patrol%20efficiency%20and%20augmenting%20China's%20overall%20military%20footprint%20in%20these%20strategically%20important%2C%20remote%20locations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Click%20here%20for%20high-res%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Click%20here%20for%20high-res%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ff3hq7r1o_helicopter-arunachal_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heliport%20also%20features%20at%20least%20three%20hangars%2C%20a%20sizeable%20apron%20area%20for%20helicopters%20to%20be%20positioned%2C%20an%20air%20traffic%20control%20facility%20and%20associated%20buildings%20and%20structures.%20Click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fj9gihj6g_helicopter-arunachal_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20high-res%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitary%20sources%20who%20are%20monitoring%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20heliport%20add%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20definitely%20military%20infrastructure%20being%20constructed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20facility%20may%20also%20have%20a%20dual-use%20function%20to%20enable%20the%20movement%20of%20civilians%20into%20the%20remote%20area.%20The%20heliport%2C%20they%20add%2C%20enhances%20Chinese%20%26quot%3Bdefensive%20and%20offensive%20operations%20%5Band%5D%20their%20reaction%20capabilities%20increase.%26quot%3B%20This%20enables%20a%20speedy%20build-up%20of%20troops%20during%20a%20contingency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fishtails%20area%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20named%20after%20the%20distinctive%20shape%20of%20the%20boundary-line%20in%20this%20area%2C%20is%20comprised%20of%20Fishtail%201%20and%20Fishtail%202.%20While%20Fishtail%201%20lies%20in%20the%20Dibang%20Valley%2C%20Fishtail%202%20is%20partly%20in%20the%20Anjaw%20district%20of%20the%20state.%20Both%20areas%20are%20considered%20'sensitive'%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20zones%20where%20China%20and%20India%20have%20differing%20perceptions%20of%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20heliport%20will%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20key%20areas%20which%20are%20considered%20'sensitive'%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lt%20General%20Pravin%20Bakshi%20(retired)%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20Eastern%20Command%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20take%20serious%20note%20and%20look%20to%20orchestrate%20a%20suitable%20response%2C%20if%20ever%20required%2C%20in%20concern%20with%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20so%20as%20to%20prevent%20any%20'grey-zone'%20warfare%20being%20efficiently%20prosecuted%20by%20the%20Chinese%20here.%26quot%3B%20Grey-Zone%20warfare%20refers%20to%20a%20form%20of%20conflict%20which%20falls%20below%20the%20threshold%20of%20conventional%20war%20while%20still%20threatening%20boundary%20lines%20through%20coercive%20means%20that%20threaten%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heliport%20under%20construction%20features%20a%20600-metre%20runway%20which%20can%20be%20used%20for%20rolling%20take-offs%20of%20helicopters%2C%20a%20technique%20used%20in%20high-altitude%20areas%20where%20there%20is%20less%20power%20available%20for%20helicopters%20to%20use.%20Despite%20this%20runway%2C%20the%20new%20heliport%20is%20situated%20in%20an%20area%20where%20the%20altitude%20is%20substantially%20lower%20than%20large%20tracts%20of%20the%20Tibetan%20plateau.%20This%20benefits%20helicopter%20operations.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20plateau%20has%20a%20disadvantage%20because%20of%20altitude%2C%20the%20general%20altitude%20in%20this%20area%20is%20in%20the%201500%20metre%20(approximately%205000%20feet)%20range%20which%20allows%20greater%20payload%20to%20be%20carried%20by%20choppers%20and%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Click%20here%20for%20high-res%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Click%20here%20for%20high-res%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Frrkft89o_helicopter-arunachal_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heliport%20under%20construction%20features%20a%20600-metre%20runway%20which%20can%20be%20used%20for%20rolling%20take-offs%20of%20helicopters.%20Click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F