cking%20operation%20with%20the%20help%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20employees%E2%80%9D%2C%20including%20high-ranking%20supervisors.%20These%20employees%20allegedly%20facilitated%20sexual%20performances%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9CFreak%20Offs%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20involved%20sex%20workers%20and%20were%20organised%20to%20include%20%E2%80%9Ccontrolled%20substances%2C%20baby%20oil%20lubricant%2C%20extra%20linens%2C%20and%20lighting.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20indictment%20does%20not%20name%20specific%20individuals%2C%20sources%20suggest%20Kristina%20Khorram%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20charged%20with%20any%20crime%2C%20may%20hold%20vital%20information%20about%20the%20operation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anybody%20is%20the%20gatekeeper%2C%20Kristina%20would%20know%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20the%20NY%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20federal%20raids%20at%20Combs'%20mansions%20uncovered%20narcotics%20and%20over%201%2C000%20bottles%20of%20baby%20oil%20and%20lubricant.%20Investigators%20have%20reportedly%20obtained%20key%20evidence%2C%20including%20text%20messages%20and%20recordings%2C%20some%20allegedly%20implicating%20Khorram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Diddy%20publicly%20praised%20Khorram%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10159056349829697%26id%3D23291809696%26set%3Da.408569254696%26locale%3Dsl_SI%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eposting%20on%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%2037-year-old%20has%20been%20his%20%E2%80%9Cright%20hand%20for%20the%20last%208%20years%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconsistently%20proven%20to%20execute%20and%20get%20s**t%20done%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CDon't%20know%20how%20I'd%20function%20without%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20allegations%20against%20Kristina%20Khorram%20have%20surfaced%20in%20a%20separate%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20rapper%20Lil%20Rod%20(real%20name%20Rodney%20Jones)%20in%20February%202024.%20In%20his%20