and%20political%20figures%20in%20Iran%20and%20Lebanon.%20Particularly%2C%20military%20commanders%20with%20battle%20experience%20fighting%20in%20Syria.%20By%20eliminating%20enough%20of%20them%2C%20Israel%20would%20weaken%20Hezbollah's%20command%20and%20control%20structure%20as%20well%20as%20strategic%20capacity.%20Making%20a%20land%20invasion%20a%20bit%20less%20difficult%20for%20Israel.%20Netanyahu%20is%20trying%20to%20soften%20them%20up%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20before%20the%20inevitable%20ground%20war.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726639860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F7p62t9fg_hassan-nasrallah-getty-_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-inside-lebanon-politics-hezbollah-iran-and-a-larger-battle-for-hegemony-6588884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lebanon's%20political%20system%20is%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20sectarian%20divisions.%20The%20country%20is%20a%20confessional%20democracy%2C%20meaning%20that%20key%20political%20and%20military%20positions%20are%20reserved%20for%20representatives%20of%20specific%20religious%20sects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-inside-lebanon-politics-hezbollah-iran-and-a-larger-battle-for-hegemony-6588884%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222024%20Hyundai%20Alcazar%20Facelift%20Review%3A%20Fortified%20for%20the%20Family!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Alcazar%20is%20Hyundai%20India's%20only%20three-row%20offering%2C%20and%20after%20more%20than%20three%20years%20on%20the%20market%2C%20it's%20received%20a%20proper%20refresh.%20Until%20now%2C%20the%20only%20major%20update%20was%20the%20replacement%20of%20the%20old%202.0-litre%20petrol%20engine%20with%20a%20smaller%20yet%20more%20powerful%201.5-litre%20turbocharged%20unit%2C%20which%20continues%20in%20the%20faceli