%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20pagers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pager%20or%20%E2%80%98beeper'%20is%20a%20small%2C%20portable%20communication%20device%20that%20receives%20short%20messages%2C%20typically%20numeric%20or%20alphanumeric%2C%20over%20a%20radio%20frequency%20signal.%20Pagers%20were%20widely%20used%20before%20cell%20phones%20became%20popular.%20It%20was%20a%20crucial%20communication%20tool%2C%20especially%20for%20professionals%20like%20doctors%2C%20journalists%2C%20technicians%2C%20and%20managers.%20It%20allowed%20them%20to%20receive%20important%20messages%2C%20even%20in%20remote%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20pagers%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20of%20a%20pager%20was%20straightforward%20yet%20efficient.%20When%20a%20message%20was%20sent%20via%20radio%20waves%2C%20the%20device%20would%20alert%20the%20user%20with%20a%20distinct%20beep.%20This%20prompt%20would%20then%20require%20the%20user%20to%20locate%20a%20nearby%20public%20or%20landline%20phone%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20technology%20progressed%2C%20pagers%20underwent%20significant%20improvements.%20The%20newer%20models%20were%20equipped%20with%20a%20small%20screen%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20display%20short%20messages%20directly%20on%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20the%201990s%2C%20mobile%20phones%20started%20to%20replace%20these%20little%20devices.%20The%20convenience%20of%20mobile%20phones%20quickly%20diminished%20the%20demand%20for%20pagers%2C%20and%20by%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20beepers%20had%20mostly%20vanished%20from%20public%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Hezbollah%20members%20still%20use%20pagers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20cyberattack%20targeting%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20revealed%20that%20pagers%2C%20which%20many%20assumed%20had%20become%20obsolete%2C%20were%20still%20in%20use%20by%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20p