te-spirals-out-of-control-after-candidate-throws-chair-at-rival%2Famp_articleshow%2F113443213.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Cop%20Changed%2C%20Officials%20Gone%2C%20But%20Kolkata%20Doctors%20Continue%20'Cease%20Work'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJunior%20doctors%20protesting%20in%20Kolkata%20against%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20medico%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20said%20late%20last%20night%20that%20they%20will%20continue%20their%20'cease%20work'%20agitation%20till%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20fulfills%20all%20their%20demands.%20They%20have%20said%20they%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20more%20discussions%20on%20the%20demands%20yet%20to%20be%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Front%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20many%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20malign%20their%20movement.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20our%20movement's%20pressure%2C%20the%20state%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20remove%20the%20Police%20Commissioner%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20North%2C%20Director%20of%20Health%20Services%20and%20Director%20of%20Medical%20Education.%20This%20is%20a%20partial%20victory%20of%20our%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20said%20that%20in%20their%20meeting%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee%20on%20Monday%2C%20there%20was%20no%20decision%20on%20their%20demand%20to%20remove%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20(Health).%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20gave%20us%20a%20verbal%20assurance%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20step%20in%20the%20direction%20so%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20also%20flagged%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20on%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20notification%20that%20said%20state-run%20hospitals%20would%20avoid%20giving%20night%20shifts%20to%20women%20doctors.%20The%20doctors%20said%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20women%20by%20creating%20a%20gender%20divide.%20Following%20the%20court's%20observations%20that%20it%20is%20the%20state's%20duty%20to%20provide%20security%2C%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal%20said%20the%20notification%20will%20be%20tweaked.%20The%20doctors%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20court's%20remarks%20on%20contractual%20staff%20being%20roped%20in%20to%20provide%20security%20at%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20has%20said%20that%20merely%20beefing%20up%20security%20at%20hospitals%20will%20not%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20till%20health%20services%20are%20improved.%20It%20has%20pressed%20for%20adequate%20recruitment%20of%20healthcare%20staff%20and%20counselling%20services%20at%20hospitals.%20%26quot%3BOrdinary%20people%20face%20problems%20due%20to%20corruption%20in%20the%20allotment%20of%20hospital%20beds%2C%20and%20shortage%20of%20life-saving%20drugs.%20We%20want%20a%20solution%20to%20all%20these%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctors'%20forum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20doctors%20said%20that%20during%20their%20meeting%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20they%20had%20demanded%20a%20college-level%20task%20force%20to%20address%20these%20problems.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20more%20discussions%20are%20needed.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20these%20demands%20will%20be%20fulfilled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20underlined%20their%20demand%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20fear%26quot%3B%20in%20medical%20colleges%20and%20democratic%20student%20union%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20announced%20from%20our%20protest%20site%20that%20patient%20welfare%20committees%20will%20be%20dissolved%2C%20but%20we%20got%20nothing%20in%20writing%20and%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20how%20these%20committees%20will%20be%20set%20up%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20said%20that%20it%20wants%20the%20governm