es.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20she%20even%20learned%20to%20walk%2C%20Shreyovi%20was%20already%20joining%20her%20father%2C%20a%20wildlife%20photographer%2C%20on%20trips%20to%20national%20parks%20and%20safaris.%20Surrounded%20by%20camera%20gear%20and%20naturalists%2C%20she%20likely%20heard%20the%20names%20of%20animals%20and%20tips%20for%20the%20perfect%20shot%20before%20learning%20her%20ABCs!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20surprise%2C%20then%2C%20that%20she%20developed%20an%20early%20fascination%20with%20cameras%20and%20yearned%20to%20hold%20one%20as%20far%20back%20as%20she%20can%20remember.%20At%20just%20two%20years%20old%2C%20she%20got%20her%20chance%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20her%20parents%2C%20who%20run%20a%20wildlife%20photography%20tourism%20company%20called%20Nature%20Wanderers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Shreyovi%20Mehta%20accompanied%20her%20parents%2C%20Kahini%20and%20Shivang%2C%20on%20many%20trips%20to%20national%20parks.%20She%20grew%20up%20immersed%20in%20wildlife%2C%20from%20the%20lush%20landscapes%20of%20Corbett%20and%20Bharatpur%20to%20an%20unforgettable%20visit%20to%20Masai%20Mara%20at%20just%20four%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20would%20watch%20her%20father%2C%20a%20wildlife%20photographer%2C%20drape%20his%20professional%20camera%20around%20their%20shoulders%2C%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20the%20perfect%20moment%20to%20capture%20animals%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%20two%2C%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20father%20let%20her%20touch%20his%20DSLR%20for%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moment%20she%20still%20vividly%20recalls%20eight%20years%20later.%20She%20even%20remembers%20it%20happened%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Ranthambore%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20at%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20Shreyovi%20clicked%20a%20stunning%20photograph%20of%20two%20peahens%20at%20Keoladeo%20National%20Park.%20That%20photo%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20runner-up%20in%20the%2010%20Years%20and%20Under%20category%20of%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20London%E2%80%99s%2060th%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%20award!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20up%20amidst%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaridabad%20residents%20Shivang%20and%20Kahini%20quickly%20noticed%20their%20daughter%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20innate%20love%20for%20nature%20and%20wildlife%2C%20and%20they%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20take%20her%20outdoors%20whenever%20possible.%20With%20Shivang%20spending%20over%20300%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20field%2C%20it%20meant%20long%20stretches%20away%20from%20the%20family.%20Taking%20Shreyovi%20along%20on%20his%20wildlife%20expeditions%20became%20not%20only%20a%20way%20for%20her%20to%20connect%20with%20nature%20but%20also%20a%20special%20opportunity%20for%20father-daughter%20bonding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreyovi%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20a%20safari.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366262%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreyovi%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20a%20safari.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20gradual%20inclination%20towards%20photography.%20She%20always%20loved%20being%20in%20the%20field%20with%20me.%20She%20saw%20equipment%20all%20around%20her%20and%20wanted%20to%20try%20her%20hand%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivang%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shreyovi%20was%20about%20four%2C%20her%20parents%20gave%20her%20Kahini%E2%80%99s%20old%20point-and-shoot%20camera%2C%20sparking%20her%20journey%20into%20photography.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20camera%20had%20a%20good%20zoom%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivang%20recalls%2C%20and%20Shreyovi%20loved%20experimenting%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20photographers%20and%20naturalists%2C%20she%20had%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363139%2Fjai-dhar-gupta-vijay-dhasmana-biosphere-rajaji-national-park-uttarakhand-rewilding-forest-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperfect%20environment%20to%20hone%20her%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20receiving%20guidance%20from%20some%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20field.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20six%2C%20she%20had%20already%20picked%20up%20her%20first%20professional%20camera%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20her%20budding%20photography%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20bit%20heavy%2C%20but%20I%20was%20so%20excited%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreyovi.%20With%20mentorship%20from%20the%20photographers%20at%20Nature%20Wanderers%2C%20Shreyovi%20began%20learning%20the%20finer%20aspects%20of%20photography%20%E2%80%94%20framing%2C%20angles%2C%20camera%20settings%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20had%20already%20visited%2010%20national%20parks%20and%20Masai%20Mara%2C%20spending%2030%20to%2040%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20wild%20on%20safaris%20and%20expeditions.%20For%20a%20young%20child%2C%20navigating%20the%20outdoors%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20easy%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20walking%20required%2C%20but%20Shreyovi%20embraced%20the%20challenge%20with%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShreyovi%20is%20quite%20hardy%20and%20resilient.%20She%20accompanies%20us%20on%20small%20hikes%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20never%20shies%20away%20from%20rough%20terrains.%20She%20is%20very%20disciplined%20and%20is%20up%20early%20daily%20to%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20proud%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20age%20of%20eight%2C%20Shreyovi%20has%20been%20waking%20up%20at%204%3A30%20am%20to%20practice%20her%20photography%20skills%20before%20school.%20She%20joins%20her%20mentors%20from%20Nature%20Wanderers%20every%20morning%20from%205%20to%206%20am%2C%20learning%20and%20refining%20her%20craft.%20This%20routine%20has%20instilled%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20discipline%20in%20her.%20On%20weekends%2C%20her%20parents%20take%20her%20to%20wetlands%20or%20nearby%20open%20spaces%20in%20Faridabad%20to%20further%20nurture%20her%20passion%20for%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%2C%20Shiv%20Nadar%20School%2C%20has%20also%20been%20highly%20supportive%20of%20her%20pursuits%2C%20say%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoughing%20it%20out%20for%20the%20perfect%20click!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Shreyovi%20visited%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20where%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20photography%20exhibition%20and%20was%20mesmerised%20by%20the%20breathtaking%20images%20on%20display%2C%20solidifying%20her%20own%20aspirations%20as%20a%20photographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20October%2C%20her%20own%20photograph%20will%20be%20featured%20in%20that%20very%20exhibition!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0