%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelops%20their%20personality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20being%20gleeful%2C%20having%20climbed%20a%20tree.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20teachers%2C%20says%20Nehal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20with%20kids%20below%20three%2C%20she%20says%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20go%20with%20the%20flow.%20You%20will%20experience%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20misses%20and%20hits.%20Take%20everything%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20part%20of%20the%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20some%20words%20of%20advice%20to%20parents%20in%20an%20increasingly%20competitive%20world%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20parenting%20as%20a%20pressure.%20Slow%20down.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20not%20be%20busy%20all%20the%20time.%20Let%20your%20children%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20beyond%20gadgets%20and%20video%20games.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelling%20teaches%20both%20you%20and%20your%20children%20mindfulness%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20present.%20It%20helps%20you%20shed%20your%20ego%20as%20you%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20you%20are%20not%20greater%20than%20nature.%20No%20school%20can%20provide%20the%20lessons%20that%20nature%20offers.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20fosters%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20bound%20by%20a%20shared%20love%20for%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nehal%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726491246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehal%20Shah%2C%20an%20avid%20traveller%2C%20began%20taking%20her%20son%20on%20her%20adventures%20and%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20outdoor%20experiences%20for%20families.%20Recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20nature-based%20experiences%20for%20children%2C%20she%20founded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366063%2Fnehal-shah-travel-with-kids-children-nature-trails-treks-experiences-toddlers-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Story%20of%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%201st%20Medical%20College%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Woman%20Doctor%20Who%20Made%20It%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3C