n%20healthcare%20startups%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20gaining%20first-hand%20experience%20in%20healthcare%20and%20health%20tech.%20Joining%20these%20startups%20from%20their%20infancy%2C%20she%20had%20a%20front-row%20understanding%20of%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20scale%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusy%20with%20work%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20her%2020s%20was%20spent%20eating%20out%20or%20cooking%20for%20herself.%20She%20constantly%20craved%20a%20good%20home-cooked%20meal%2C%20just%20like%20the%20ones%20her%20mother%20used%20to%20make.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20roots%20and%20the%20food%20I%20grew%20up%20eating.%20Every%20time%20I%20visited%20home%20in%20Kochi%2C%20I%20brought%20back%20staples%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powders)%2C%20which%20made%20cooking%20a%20meal%20very%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20of%20Tocco%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20of%20Tocco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20consistent%20and%20convenient%20supply%20of%20food%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reshma%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20hectic%20schedule%20coupled%20with%20late%20nights%20led%20to%20lots%20of%20restaurant%20meals.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20Reshma%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20PCOS%20(Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome).%20This%20diagnosis%20triggered%20her%20search%20for%20healthier%2C%20authentic%2C%20home-cooked%20regional%20food.%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20like%20it%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%2C%20Annu%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20faced%20the%20same%20dilemma%20%E2%80%94%20failing%20to%20find%20meals%20that%20bottled%20the%20memories%20of%20Kerala.%20Long%20discussions%20between%20the%20sisters%20led%20to%20Reshma%20creating%20experience%20boxes%20in%202021%2C%20offering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20Kerala%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekends.%20Prepared%20in%20her%20Mumbai%20kitchen%2C%20one%20dish%20clearly%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20banana%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20decided%20to%20sell%20these%20chips%20under%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emeen%20gurry%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20fish%20curry)%2C%20as%20a%20homage%20to%20their%20shared%20memories%20around%20the%20dining%20table.%20Every%20weekend%2C%20she%20curated%20different%20meal%20boxes%20while%20continuing%20her%20job%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20MeenGurry%20Memories%2C%20Reshma%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20do%20something%20to%20promote%20chefs%20like%20her%20mother%20U