I%20then%20asked%20my%20mother%20to%20make%20her%20famous%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle%2C%20a%20childhood%20favourite%20of%20many.%20I%20packaged%20it%20and%20started%20selling%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Emulga%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(gun%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%2C%20and%20other%20products%20were%20also%20introduced.%20Reshma%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20then%20created%20a%20platform%20to%20sell%20these%20nostalgic%20products%2C%20naming%20it%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98The%20Orange%20Candy%20Co%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20sense%20because%2C%20for%20Reshma%2C%20the%20ultimate%20symbol%20of%20nostalgia%20was%20the%20orange%20candies%20she%20shared%20with%20her%20sister%20during%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tocco%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20pack%20this%20childhood%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20box%20for%20other%20people%20to%20enjoy.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20onboarding%20the%20first%20two%20chefs%2C%20Reshma%20brought%20in%20more%2C%20expanding%20the%20platform%20to%20include%20over%2016%20chefs%20from%20different%20cities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20They%20offer%20snacks%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20jackfruit%20chips%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshankarpali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sweet%20snack)%3Cem%3E%2C%20masalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20sambar%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20podi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powder)%2C%20pickles%20like%20prawn%2C%20cut%20mango%2C%20homemade%20curd%20chilli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuli%20inji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ginger%20pickle)%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2058-year-old%20Uma%20Suresh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20cooking%20since%20she%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20Tocco%20has%20given%20new%20meaning%20to%20her%20